  "description": "All 8 voices in full-algorithmic territory (blend > 0.7). Modal resonators at maximum inharmonicity, Karplus-Strong with string-to-snare blend in the middle zone, Phase Distortion at extremes. XVC global amount at 0.85 with all four routes active — the kit develops autonomous rhythmic intelligence. Evades acoustic reference entirely.",
